-- Aramco Awards Three Seismic Contracts to China BGP, Riyadh Says
-- B y   M o u r a d   H a r o u t u n i a n
-- 2012-01-14T08:16:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-14/aramco-awards-three-seismic-contracts-to-china-bgp-riyadh-says.html
Saudi Arabian Oil Co., known as
Aramco, awarded three contracts to  China ’s BGP Inc. to conduct a
seismic survey to explore for hydrocarbons in the kingdom,  Al-
Riyadh  reported, citing unidentified oil industry officials.  The seismic survey, which will cover an area from the
southern Rub Al Khali desert to the border with  Iraq , aims to
raise the kingdom’s output capacity to 15 million barrels a day
by 2020, the newspaper added.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mourad Haroutunian in Riyadh at 
 mharoutunian@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Shaji Mathew at 
 shajimathew@bloomberg.net  